类 LocalFile.Thumbnail

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ciscowebex.androidsdk.message.LocalFile.Thumbnail
  • 封闭类:
    LocalFile

    public static class LocalFile.Thumbnail
extends java.lang.Object
    A data type represents a thumbnail of this local file. The thumbnail typically is an image file to provide preview of the local file without opening.
    从以下版本开始:
    1.4.0
